Data downloader & parser¶

biodb_team_3.mapping_parser_v2.get_data(url)[source]¶

A function to get data from url (‘http://www.uniprot.org/docs/mimtosp.txt’) and parse it to a list of lists contains OMIM IDs, genes or proteins names and uniprot IDs.
